{
  "stem": "27509.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For that, you needed a Russian transit visa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was a horse of a different caliber.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "To ask to go-- to get out of Russia was tantamount of saying, we don't want to live under the communist regime.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was treason, in terms of their ideological understanding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And yet, there was so little to lose that some people decided they will take a chance.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What can it be?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew that they played a trick in Lemberg.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As soon as they moved in there, at the end of, in the end of September, beginning of October, they put a notice in the paper of the travel agency, of the official travel agency, that everybody who has got [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] relatives overseas and wants to join them should register at the Orbis office.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people, in their innocence, queued for days and registered.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they took all those lists and called the people in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said to them, it's not good enough for you here under our regime, is it?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All right, we will send you somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we won't send you where you want to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You will go to, to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they packed them up and sent them to Siberia, all of them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we knew it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And yet, we have taken-- some of us were brave enough to take the first steps and say, we'll take a chance.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we, we also knew that the people who had the certificates in, in, in Wilno got transit and went to Odessa.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was not altogether an impossibility.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had a precedent where certain transit visas were obtained.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was one of the first to apply, one of the very first to apply.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we waited.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
